reviewText: I'm a beginner and thought I could learn something from anyone. This dvd is very poor quality, including the packaging, for $40. More can be learned from You Tube. Very amateurish production and I believe it was made to rip people off when the $ amount doesn't justify the content of the dvd. Sherman Clinton.
Disappointed, more like a YouTube downloaded clips compilation. Poorly edited, and VCR quality.
